name: Stormtrooper Cadet
Lore: 'After months of intense training, a trooper is paired with a veteran soldier. While providing support during field operations, the new trooper masters Imperial military tactics.',
Text: 'Deploys free to same site as an Imperial leader. Adds 1 to power of one non-unique Imperial warrior present. When forfeited at same site as an Imperial ''veteran'' (a leader or non-cadet trooper), also satisfies all remaining attrition against you.',
